allery link=\"file\"]\r\n\r\nMore than anything, I was trying to play around with different database and see if we could extract something meaningful from the, while keep the micro/macro relationship more respectful of a particular node.\r\n\r\nAt the end, this is really not a final piece, just a stepping stone to something else.','A Book About: Jorge','','inherit','open','open','','876-revision-4','','','2012-10-09 18:42:18','2012-10-09 18:42:18','',876,'http://thejsj.com/uncategorized/876-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(909,1,'2012-10-09 22:05:31','2012-10-09 22:05:31','','PdfExport40','','inherit','open','open','','pdfexport40','','','2012-10-09 22:05:31','2012-10-09 22:05:31','',869,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/PdfExport40.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(910,1,'2012-10-09 22:05:37','2012-10-09 22:05:37','I wish to make a book that would design itself.\n\nThis book is generated by a script that goes on generating forms that are added and subtracted throughout the book.\n\nEvery page, one more element is added, until the middle is reached. After that, one element is removed.\n\n[gallery link=\"file\"]\n\nThe problem with this is that this is all pure form. There is no content, narrative or even inherent meaning. I like the way it looks. But itÂ doesn\'tÂ say anything.\n\nHow can we make something that is generated say somethingÂ substancial, without the meaning being already there? How can me generate narrative?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/PdfExport40.pdf\">PdfExport40</a>','A Book That Makes Itself','','inherit','open','open','','869-autosave','','','2012-10-09 22:05:37','2012-10-09 22:05:37','',869,'http://thejsj.com/uncategorized/869-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(911,1,'2012-10-09 18:34:30','2012-10-09 18:34:30','I wish to make a book that would design itself.\r\n\r\nThis book is generated by a script that goes on generating forms that are added and subtracted throughout th