 of people around the area. I met and talked to people who were curious about what I was doing, people I had to interact with because of my instructions, or just people who wanted to get some attention from the camera. These encounters with the people out on the street provide much of the richness of this video.\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"file\" include=\"1041, 1040, 1039, 1038, 1037\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','This is Your Script','','inherit','open','open','','1032-revision-3','','','2012-11-15 16:50:21','2012-11-15 16:50:21','',1032,'http://thejsj.com/uncategorized/1032-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(1049,1,'2013-01-03 22:11:18','2013-01-03 22:11:18','','Index','','publish','open','open','','index','','','2013-01-03 22:11:18','2013-01-03 22:11:18','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?page_id=1049',0,'page','',0),(1085,1,'2012-04-11 03:22:03','2012-04-11 03:22:03','','Portfolio','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-5','','','2012-04-11 03:22:03','2012-04-11 03:22:03','',46,'http://thejsj.com/uncategorized/46-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(1051,1,'2013-01-03 22:13:07','2013-01-03 22:13:07','','*****','Surprise #1','publish','open','open','','1051','','','2013-05-21 23:23:07','2013-05-21 23:23:07','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?p=1051',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1052,1,'2013-01-03 22:14:33','2013-01-03 22:14:33',' ','','No, this page is NOT about me!','publish','open','open','','1052','','','2013-05-21 23:23:07','2013-05-21 23:23:07','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?p=1052',11,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1053,1,'2013-01-03 22:14:33','2013-01-03 22:14:33','','*****','Surprise #2','publish','open','open','','1053','','','2013-05-21 23:23:07','2013-05-21 23:23:07','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?p=1053',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1055,1,'2013-01-03 22:24:15','2013-01-03 22:24:15','','DTAVZ','Data Visualization','publish','open','open','','dtavz','','','2013-05-21 23:23:07','2013-05-21 23:23:07','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?p=1055',4,'