 happens one day at time, hour by hour, minute by minute. It all goes by so quickly, so slowly. It seems possible at every second, you just need to start.','Clinging','','draft','open','open','','','','','2013-03-23 20:48:47','2013-03-23 20:48:47','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?p=1305',0,'post','',0),(1277,1,'2013-02-18 21:15:42','2013-02-18 21:15:42','','I Love Islands - JSJ','','inherit','open','open','','i-love-islands-jsj','','','2013-02-18 21:15:42','2013-02-18 21:15:42','',0,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/I-Love-Islands-JSJ.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1278,1,'2013-02-05 21:17:48','2013-02-05 21:17:48','A poster.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/I-Love-Islands-JSJ.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1277\" alt=\"I Love Islands - JSJ\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/I-Love-Islands-JSJ-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" /></a>','I love Islands','','publish','closed','closed','','i-love-islands','','','2013-02-18 21:18:37','2013-02-18 21:18:37','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?post_type=piece&#038;p=1278',0,'piece','',0),(1280,1,'2013-02-18 21:27:58','2013-02-18 21:27:58','','By..','','inherit','open','open','','by','','','2013-02-18 21:27:58','2013-02-18 21:27:58','',0,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/By...jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1281,1,'2013-02-18 21:28:02','2013-02-18 21:28:02','','Glossy','','inherit','open','open','','glossy','','','2013-02-18 21:28:02','2013-02-18 21:28:02','',0,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Glossy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1282,1,'2013-02-18 21:28:17','2013-02-18 21:28:17','','Me','','inherit','open','open','','me','','','2013-02-18 21:28:17','2013-02-18 21:28:17','',0,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Me.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1283,1,'2013-02-18 21:28:21','2013-02-18 21:28:21','','Notes on Language','','inherit','open','op